<li>UV-C light leaves behind no chemical smell</li>
</ul>
<h4>The bad</h4>
<ul>
<li>Not effective on porous or softer surfaces</li>
<li>Requires recharging</li>
<li>Can't really validate whether or not it's effective without lab analysis</li>
</ul>
